OL,7,FFamilies who lost loved ones during
OL,8,Fthe pandemic have called for all the
OL,9,FWhatsapp messages exchanged between
OL,10,Fministers and officials to be
OL,11,Fpublished.
OL,13,FThe lawyer representing the made the
OL,14,Frequest on the UK Covid-19 Inquiry's
OL,15,Ffinal day in Wales "so that the Welsh
OL,16,Fpeople can see what their government
OL,17,Fwas using informal messaging for."
