OL,7,FKirsten Heaven said: "The Welsh
OL,8,FGovernment has repeatedly shirked a
OL,9,Fgranular inspection of Welsh decision-
OL,10,Fmaking by refusing to open itself up
OL,11,Fto scrutiny in a Welsh-specific
OL,12,Finquiry, seeking instead to blame the
OL,13,FUK Government.
OL,15,F"It is also regrettable that this
OL,16,Finquiry and indeed this module has
OL,17,Fbeen forced to spend so much time
OL,18,Fasking about missing evidence and
OL,19,Fdestroyed Whatsapps."
