OL,7,FOver the past week, the inquiry has
OL,8,Fheard how the messages of the First
OL,9,FMinister, , and the former Health
OL,10,FMinister, Vaughan Gething, have been
OL,11,F"lost", unrecovered or deleted.
OL,13,FOn Monday, Mr Gething told the inquiry
OL,14,Fthat it was .
OL,16,FOn Thursday, seven representatives of
OL,17,Fcore participants including bereaved
OL,18,Ffamilies and vulnerable groups gave
OL,19,Fclosing statements.
