OL,7,FThey reflected on what the inquiry's
OL,8,Ftime in Wales has so far revealed, and
OL,9,Fwhat they feel the inquiry should
OL,10,Ffocus on going forward.
OL,12,FMs Heaven added: "In all the other
OL,13,Fmodules you've heard some reflection
OL,14,Fand some acceptance that mistakes were
OL,15,Fmade and it is deeply worrying to the
OL,16,FWelsh bereaved that their government
OL,17,Fseems incapable of doing the same.
OL,19,F"This ought to raise a real concern
OL,20,Fthat lessons have not truly been
OL,21,Flearnt here in Wales.
