OL,7,F"The Welsh Government's initial
OL,8,Fresponse can be summarised in three
OL,9,Fwordings: passive, slow and
OL,10,Fdisjointed."
OL,12,FThe lawyer representing people with
OL,13,Fdisabilities told the inquiry that
OL,14,FWales was "not resilient", adding that
OL,15,F"the system was vulnerable, not
OL,16,Fpeople".
