OL,7,FBut Danny Friedman KC said Wales'
OL,8,Fproblem during the pandemic was that
OL,9,Fit was "too small, both in terms of
OL,10,Fthe power it held and its capacity to
OL,11,Fdo things differently."
OL,13,FHe added: "It was too small not to be
OL,14,Ftaken for granted by Westminster. The
OL,15,Fresult was Wales being informed about
OL,16,Fdecisions rather than being consulted
OL,17,Fupon them on numerous occasions.
