OL,7,FHe said: "Sir Frank Atherton and Dr
OL,8,FOrford did not have the difficult
OL,9,Fministerial client that Professors
OL,10,FWhitty and Vallance had, but it seems
OL,11,Fthat they did not make clear the
OL,12,Fgravity of Covid-19 as early and as
OL,13,Frigorously as they should have."
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, the First Minister told
OL,16,Fthe inquiry that he "regrets
OL,17,Feverything that led to loss of life".
OL,19,FBut Mark Drakeford added that he was
OL,20,Fnot at the inquiry to "justify", but
OL,21,Fto "explain".
