OL,7,F"I don't think the test for me is
OL,8,Fwhether I got everything right,
OL,9,Fbecause I don't think anybody could
OL,10,Fpossibly pass such a test," he said.
OL,12,FAndrew Kinnier KC, representing the
OL,13,FWelsh Government, said on Thursday:
OL,14,F"To have taken one reasonable course
OL,15,Fwhen an alternative reasonable option
OL,16,Fwas also available does not make the
OL,17,Fcourse taken wrong or in some way
OL,18,Fflawed.
